  <span id="freeText4495018130180231612" style="display:none">Beautiful review, Matthew and once again, so wise and profound. I think Marquez, like how some writers do, must have looked upon it with fondness simply because as a creator, he must have felt that without "Leaf Storm", the whole world of Macondo in his greatest triumph would not have taken shape.</span>
